Add fix for riscv libdirs

On riscv, we have the following symlinks:

/lib64/lp64d -> .
/usr/lib64/lp64d -> .

In the case where src and dst are both symlinks, check to see if they
both point to the same relative path under each directory. If so, assume
it is safe to skip.
